  "text": "In order to maintain optimal patient satisfaction, implement sight into the service quality of the health care professionals in both public healthcare hospitals. On average, the patients have been utilizing the services of both public hospitals for at least 9.5 years, which means that they are appropriate and suitable to assess the service quality delivered by healthcare professionals employed by the institution. The findings re-vealed that patients expect more service quality than what they are receiving, which is a starting point in fulfilling the vision of SERHA and this is no different from what obtains for the Jamaica Police [CITATION_1] .",
